# Commit Message Template
# Format: component: concise action (no period)
# Examples:
#   ssh: replace static authorized keys with sops managed
#   virtualization: add kvm + qemu toggles
#   docs: add manual commit checklist
#   flake.lock: update
#
# Lines starting with # are ignored.


# Checklist (run BEFORE committing, remove or leave commented):
# [ ] nix fmt
# [ ] nix flake check
# [ ] nix build .#nixosConfigurations.${HOST}.config.system.build.toplevel (if NixOS system touched)
# [ ] nix build .#darwinConfigurations.${MAC_HOST}.system (if macOS host touched)
# [ ] nix build .#homeConfigurations."${USER}@${HOST}".activationPackage (if home modules touched)
# [ ] git diff --cached --name-only (review staged files)
# [ ] secrets updated via sops (no plaintext secrets)
# [ ] commit message uses component: description pattern
